'''''Próxima Estación: Esperanza''''' is an album by [[Manu Chao]].  It was released in [[Europe]] in 2000. It was released in the [[United States]] on June 5, 2001 on [[Virgin Records]].  Chao and others sing in [[Arabic language|Arabic]], [[English language|English]], [[French language|French]], [[Portuguese language|Portuguese]], and [[Spanish language|Spanish]] on this album.
