==Trivia==
The name comes from a sample of an announcement for the [[Esperanza]] ("hope") [[Madrid Metro]] [[List of Madrid metro stations|station]].
However the Metro speaker sued for the rights of the unauthorized sample.

The song "Me Gustas Tú" was featured on the soundtrack to the 2003 film ''[[Once Upon a Time in Mexico]]''.

